[thinking] **Considering platform initialization**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm facing an issue where `com.sun.jna.Platform` is initialized during the build process on Linux, but then changing `os.name` at runtime doesn’t affect the static `osType`. This leads to test failures because the holder defaults to X11. But then I wonder if the generated class indicates that the build or JVM agent actually ran on a Mac. It's possible the `MacWindowUtils` anonymous class is active here. I need to clarify this.
